    xQTLquery_sampleByTissue

    xQTLquery_sampleByTissue.Rd

    query sample's details with a specifc tissue name

    Usage

    xQTLquery_sampleByTissue(
  tissueSiteDetail = "Liver",
  dataType = "RNASEQ",
  datasetId = "gtex_v8",
  recordPerChunk = 200,
  pathologyNotesCategories = FALSE
)

    Arguments

    tissueSiteDetail

    dataType

    A character string. Options: "RNASEQ" (default), "WGS", "WES", "OMNI".

    datasetId

    A character string. Options: "gtex_v8" (default), "gtex_v7".

    recordPerChunk

    A integer value (1-2000). number of records fetched per request (default: 200).

    pathologyNotesCategories

    Default: pathologyNotes info is ignored.

    Value

    returen sample information

    Examples

    # \donttest{
  sampleInfo <- xQTLquery_sampleByTissue(tissueSiteDetail="Liver", datasetId="gtex_v8",
                                         pathologyNotesCategories=TRUE  )
